title: FrouFrouWhatWereYouDoingInTheOffice
position: -248,-453
---

Archie: What were you doing in the office?
FrouFrou: I had been in the ladies room with my Mistress - she and I are rarely separated, you see - when that heathen man came in. How I despise him! So as he entered I slipped out the door and hid in the office. Then with all that happened afterwards…well, I was just too scared to move! Perhaps I am a coward for not being with my Mistress, but there is something ever so sinister about him. ‘Tis a shame I have no strong, brave dog in my life, such as yourself, else I might not feel so afraid. 

