title: FrouFrouDoYouKnowHim
position: -39,-503
---

Archie: Does your mistress have anything connection to the murdered man?
FrouFrou: Yes, though we should hardly associate with one so beneath our pedigree. Often he came to our residence. I hated it. I sleep on a silk pillow beside my Mistress every night without fail, except when *he* shows up. Then I am locked out of the bedroom! Did you ever hear of such injustice?

